  • Constructor Details

    • Lab

      public Lab(String inputFile, StringBuilder sb) throws FileNotFoundException
      Initializes a Lab given a certain number of printers, indicated in our inputFile, and a StringBuilder we'll be using
      Parameters:
      inputFile - The file from where we'll know how many printers will there be in our Lab
      sb - The StringBuilder where we'll be updating all our information about our Lab
      Throws:
      FileNotFoundException - if the input file can't be found
      Requires:
      The inputFile to have only a positive integer value greater than 0 and sb != null
